WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.260
As you dream up your ideas, it is
important to be passionate about them.

00:00:04.260 --> 00:00:07.240
It is never a good idea to create
a startup just because you want to

00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:08.510
create a startup.

00:00:08.510 --> 00:00:11.300
Create a startup because you
want to solve a problem that

00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:12.970
keeps you up at night.

00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:15.720
Successful companies start
from a good idea and

00:00:15.720 --> 00:00:18.860
a good idea might be
one of these things.

00:00:18.860 --> 00:00:20.480
Solve a novel problem.

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:22.360
Google did that with search.

00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:24.230
Extend the current solution.

00:00:24.230 --> 00:00:27.210
Udacity does that by providing
an affordable on-demand

00:00:27.210 --> 00:00:29.580
technical education for jobs.

00:00:29.580 --> 00:00:31.370
Disrupt an industry.

00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:34.440
Uber provides an easier
way to share a ride.

00:00:34.440 --> 00:00:37.500
In the next video,
Chris is going to share types of idea

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:39.390
that might help you
come up with your idea.

